This method and the following Verify are used when you expect to get multiple messages back. In this case you&#39;re only expecting a single message so you could just use the Verify on its own  e.g..

verifyEquals(&quot;Short name is mandatory&quot;, lpap_General.Validation_MessageReadonlyTextfield.getText(), MessageKeys.YOUR_MESSAGE);

